  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across 5 flow-speed combinations. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; required and achieved levels are documented. Decision: Accepted subject to monitoring. NOTE (adversarial): the ContextOfUse description enumerates operating ranges in prose but neither hasApplicabilityConstraint nor hasOperatingEnvelope is formally linked, leaving the model's bounded domain of validity unspecified in machine-readable form.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-absolute-threshold",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-hemolysis-cou2-accepted",
