      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to Navier-Stokes equations; hemolysis transport equation verified by benchmark analytic solution. Sub-model coupling verification incomplete, reducing achieved level by one gradation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent performed; grid convergence index reported for hemolysis index QOI across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "GCI computed on three systematically refined meshes at two of five operating points. Remaining three points show monotonic convergence but GCI not formally reported, limiting achieved level to 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
